      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This chassis has been vetted for structural integrity, including reinforced subframe mounting points and refreshed trailing arm bushings to maintain precise toe and camber alignment. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping rates, offering a balanced roll center and exceptional turn-in bite. This is a well-sorted, driver-focused example that prioritizes mechanical synchronization and atmospheric induction performance.",
